  "date": "2016-08-31 09:55", 
  "link": "http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p811512/", 
  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p811512/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/24fc7672f0bcb956af43d8c53be3f93b.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t注：加粗+下划线代表双语对照重点。</p>\n<p>\n\t《<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">好莱坞报道（The Hollywood Reporter）》近日评出了9月到元旦前最值得期待的37部电影。是不是有小伙伴觉得人生又有寄托了？</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">是的，人生四大喜，洞房、中举、故知、看片。为了造福人间，博爱如英大当然给大家扒来了。这里为大家奉上完整榜单，先精选介绍10部英大最期待的：</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">1. 《佩小姐的奇幻城堡》<span style=\"color: #008000;\">Miss Peregrine's Home for&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Peculiar\" target=\"_blank\">Peculiar</a></strong></span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\">&nbsp;Children</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/63174d4ab8e803e72b6d662af1784e42.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Eva Green&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/reunite\" target=\"_blank\">reunites</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;with Tim Burton to play the&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/titular\" target=\"_blank\">titular</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/headmistress\" target=\"_blank\">headmistress</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;of the&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/orphanage\" target=\"_blank\">orphanage</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;full of magical misfits. Fox&rsquo;s&nbsp;</span><u><strong>fantasy flick</strong></u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">, based on Ransom Riggs' 2011 novel, follows a teenage boy who is transported to an island where he must help protect a group of&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/orphan\" target=\"_blank\">orphans</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;with special powers from creatures out to destroy them.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">伊娃&middot;格林和蒂姆&middot;波顿再次合作，她饰演的是标题中的佩小姐，她是一家孤儿院的院长，院里住满了各种魔幻的怪人。这部福克斯的<u><strong>奇幻电影</strong></u>改编自Ransom Rigg在2011年写的小说，讲述一个男孩被传送到了一座岛上，并帮助一众拥有超能力的孤儿抵挡外界想消灭他们的生物。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">北美上映时间：9月30日。中国大陆上映时间：10月有望。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">2. 《但丁密码》</strong><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Inferno\" target=\"_blank\">Inferno</a></span></strong></span></p>\n<div>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/8c355d4afb0afb85ab8597ed20882bf4.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Tom Hanks is back as&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/symbologist\" target=\"_blank\">symbologist</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;Robert Langdon in the third&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/installment\" target=\"_blank\">installment</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;of Dan Brown's best-selling series, in which he teams up with a doctor he hopes will help him recover his memories to stop a deadly global&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/plot\" target=\"_blank\">plot</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;related to the&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/medieval\" target=\"_blank\">medieval</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/philosopher\" target=\"_blank\">philosopher</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;Dante. Following 2006's The Da Vinci Code and 2009's Angels & Demons, Ron Howard again directs the <u><strong>adaptation</strong></u>.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">汤姆&middot;汉克斯又回来演符号学家罗伯特&middot;兰登了，这回演的是丹&middot;布朗畅销系列里的第三本。片中，他将与一位医生搭对，他希望这位医生能帮他恢复记忆，从而阻止一场与中世纪哲学家但丁有关的世界级致命阴谋。继2006年的《达芬奇密码》和2009年的《天使与魔鬼》之后，这一次的<u><strong>改编</strong></u>同样是由郎&middot;霍华德担任导演。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">北美上映时间：10月28日。中国大陆上映时间：有望同期上映。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">3. 《怪物召唤》<span style=\"color: #008000;\">A Monster Calls</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/8ba6763111bf6ffbca979d349c902c6d.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">The adaptation of Patrick Ness&rsquo; award-winning children's fantasy novel is about a young boy who&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/attempt\" target=\"_blank\">attempts</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;to deal with <u><strong>bullying</strong></u> at the hands of his classmates, and his mother's <u><strong>terminal illness</strong></u>, by escaping into a fantastical world through the&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/guidance\" target=\"_blank\">guidance</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;of a tree monster.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">这部电影改编自Patrick Ness的获奖儿童奇幻小说，讲的是一个小男孩的故事，他需要忍受班上同学的<u><strong>欺凌</strong></u>，同时还要面对母亲的<u><strong>绝症</strong></u>。为了应对生活中的问题，他在一个树妖的引导下进入了一个奇幻的世界。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">北美上映时间：10月14日。中国大陆上映时间：未知。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">4. 《神奇动物在哪里》<span style=\"color: #008000;\">Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/6f5e760274e3f1be25de9c336df07b75.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Eddie Redmayne stars in the Harry Potter spinoff as Newt Scamander, a magician on a search for the rare and unusual supernatural creatures of the movie's title. It also tells the story of the American magical community dealing with&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/prejudice\" target=\"_blank\">prejudice</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">in the form of the No-Maj (or &quot;no magic&quot;) New Salem&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Philanthropic\" target=\"_blank\">Philanthropic</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;Society, a&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/sinister\" target=\"_blank\">sinister</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;group out to kill wizards and witches. The movie, directed by David Yates &mdash; who directed the final four Harry Potter movies &mdash; marks the screenwriting&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/debut\" target=\"_blank\">debut</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;of Potter creator J.K. Rowling.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">小雀斑埃迪&middot;雷德梅恩将在《哈利&middot;波特》的衍生剧中出演Newt Scamander，他是个在寻找影片名称中这些罕见超自然生物的魔法师。影片还讲述了美国的法师世界是如何与新塞勒姆反魔法慈善社的偏见做斗争的，后者是一个四处追杀魔法师的邪恶组织。这部电影的导演是大卫&middot;叶茨，《哈利&middot;波特》的最后4部电影都是他导演的。这部电影是原著作者J.K.罗琳作为电影编剧的处女作。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">北美上映时间：11月18日。中国大陆上映时间：有望引进。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">5. 《火车上的女孩》<span style=\"color: #008000;\">The Girl on the Train</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/70a7ee3cf740b26f764836ace0469a20.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">This adaptation of Paula Hawkins&rsquo; best-seller stars Emily Blunt as a troubled woman who becomes fascinated by a seemingly perfect couple whose home she passes while riding the train &mdash; until one day, she thinks she witnesses a murder.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">这部电影改编自Paula Hawkins的畅销小说，主演是艾米丽&middot;勃朗特。她饰演的是一个深陷困境的女人，她一次次在乘火车的时候经过一家看起来十分美满的家庭，逐渐对这对夫妻的生活着迷，但之后她似乎目睹了一场谋杀案，而这一切也跟着改变。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">北美上映时间：10月7日。中国大陆上映时间：未知。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">6. 《奇异博士》</span><span style=\"color: #008000;\">Doctor Strange</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/cb49525d2f1be2791e3d9e3e3d4c7e8e.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">The Marvel film stars Benedict Cumberbatch as the titular <u><strong>Sorcerer Supreme</strong></u>, and Tilda Swinton as The Ancient One.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">卷福本尼迪克特&middot;康伯巴奇将在这部漫威电影中饰演标题中的<u><strong>大法师</strong></u>，而他的师父至尊法师则由蒂尔达&middot;斯文顿反串。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">北美上映时间：11月4日。中国大陆上映时间：有望引进。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">7. 《谍影侠探：永不回头》<span style=\"color: #008000;\">Jack Reacher: Never Go Back</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/5ca8acc90c4aa42bd5e7d872bbd889c1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">The sequel sees Tom Cruise&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/reprise\" target=\"_blank\">reprising</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;his role as the titular army officer-turned-</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/drifter\" target=\"_blank\">drifter</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">在这部续集中，汤姆&middot;克鲁斯将再次饰演这个被用作电影标题的角色，他原本是个军人，而现在是个流浪汉。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">北美上映时间：10月21日。中国大陆上映时间：有望引进。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">8. 《逗鸟外传：萌宝满天飞》<span style=\"color: #008000;\">Storks</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/2e906e65b3bfb5101e6c756d4dbdad71.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">The film is set in a world where&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/stork\" target=\"_blank\">storks</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;no longer deliver babies, but rather packages for a global internet&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/retail\" target=\"_blank\">retail</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;giant &mdash; until the company&rsquo;s top stork&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/accidentally\" target=\"_blank\">accidentally</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/activate\" target=\"_blank\">activates</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;the dusty Baby Making Machine and produces an&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/authorized\" target=\"_blank\">authorized</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;baby.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">在这部电影的世界里，送子鸟们不再只送孩子了，他们还帮一家互联网全球零售巨头送快递。有一天，公司的头牌送子鸟不小心启动了布满灰尘的宝宝制造机，并授权生产了一个宝宝。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">北美上映时间：9月23日。中国大陆上映时间：同！一！天！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">9. 《斯诺登》<span style=\"color: #008000;\">Snowden</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/37eef6bba66e1d76f7983ea99c453c62.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">The biopic stars Joseph Gordon-Levitt as NSA&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/leaker\" target=\"_blank\">leaker</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;Edward Snowden.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">在这部电影中，囧瑟夫将饰演美国国家安全局的泄密者斯诺登。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">北美上映时间：9月16日。中国大陆上映时间：未知。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">10. 《动物园好声音》<span style=\"color: #008000;\">Sing</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/ec9b8cab822bdd0218b0a756cb0835d7.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Matthew McConaughey leads Universal&rsquo;s animated film as a theater-owning&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/koala\" target=\"_blank\">koala</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;who attempts to reverse his fortunes by holding the world's greatest singing competition.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">马修&middot;麦康纳将在这部环球影业的动画电影中担任主声优，他演的是一只经营着一家剧院的考拉，这只考拉试图通过举世界上最棒的歌唱比赛来扭转自己的境遇。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">北美上映时间：12月21日。中国大陆上映时间：未知。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">其他27部如下：</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">《魔发精灵》</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/d9a4ab0d93e1aa9aeb589fcc79699a26.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;《攀比邻居》</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/b518ff39a8d74cd86112ecbf545b0d0e.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">《会计刺客》</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/193ccd9397413063f35085e955c5a268.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">《一个国家的诞生》</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/a74a5170322c184df8ef005f7316dbc6.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">《深海浩劫》</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/df90013443eb5ae35b037cc108260c0f.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">《萨利船长》</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/30/4de05932f72d061aa24afa5e2d9a5eb3.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /><